<div class="circle circle-nowo"></div>

<div class="content">
  <div class="textBox">
    <div class="texBox--phrase">
      <h2 class= "texBox--title mb-4" id="textBoxSlogan" data-aos="fade-right" data-aos-duration="3000">As melhores ofertas de<br>
        <span id="letterSlogan" class="letter letter--nowo ml-md-3">NOWO</span>
      </h2>
    </div>

    <p data-aos="fade-down" data-aos-duration="3000" class="text-justify text">
      Com apenas <strong>21,25 €/mês</strong> aproveite a promoção de: 

      <ul class="ul-promo" data-aos="flip-up" data-aos-duration="2000">
